In the same way as Middlebury College,the tuition fees at Epitech are expensives.

In both, Middlebury College and Epitech, your grades are represented by a GPA.

There is one more thing Epitech and Middlebury College have in common, you can work for the school in exchnage of a salary.

Unlike Middlebury College, Epitech do not propose a lot of extra activities.

Contrary to Middlebury College, Epitech do not permit to have a scholorship

